title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell.
EB: The system should be able to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell without throwing an exception.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Insert a table inside one of the grid cells.
3. Insert another table inside another grid cell.
